# Weekend-Planner

Weekend Planner is an API made for Practeon for making weekend trip with low budget by adding more people in the trip.

## All Trip [/dashboard]
This is page where alll the trips happeing in the coming dates will be diplayed.
### List all the Trips [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "trip_id": "10",
                "when": "25/09/2016",
                "where": "Nandi Hills",
                "type": "Hill station",
                "number_days": "3",
                "space_left": "3"
            }
            {
                "trip_id": "15",
                "when": "26/09/2016",
                "where": "Thanjavur",
                "type": "Temple",
